6-10T03:07:18.000Z","msg":"中共寧願香港大飢荒<br />\n<br />\n餓死曬750萬人<br />\n<br />\n都唔會比個黨亡"},{"pid":"ae474d955a95e0debbd7ca3ef8157c077d243df2","tid":2058151,"uid":205733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b5203c0e588843698120fabc69fa1c2af146ee70","tid":2058151,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T03:05:08.000Z","msg":"大幅加稅<br />\n減福利<br />\n黑警軍費一定有加無減"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T03:11:01.000Z","msg":"係，可以預見的<br />\n但要知道港共政府主要收入係印花稅同利得稅<br />\n若果繼續救垃圾企業，社會運動未完<br />\n印花稅同利得稅會大減<br />\n若果薪俸稅大加+cut綜援/公屋/醫療福利<br />\n將會有更多淺藍，甚至深藍歸黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de9365d1e4fe787a2148713cddcdb3c7ee062063","tid":2058151,"uid":205733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a4171507c6b2dd121074acd809f9968dcbfd975","tid":2058151,"uid":83523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T03:07:18.000Z","msg":"中共寧願香港大飢荒<br />\n<br />\n餓死曬750萬人<br />\n<br />\n都唔會比個黨亡"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T03:12:29.000Z","msg":"所以要爭取埋 BNO/港人移民權利<br />\n務求中共死，我地唔死"},{"pid":"2e4c461393d48779532caa6807e45f86b6ba7076","tid":2058151,"uid":205733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"afef41dadbd9a5f44732b8afad7144f9c05b90b8","tid":2058151,"uid":205733,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"cb35cd6f2a2f69339f6922e5732871388b4e8e37","tid":2058151,"uid":345502,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"10a954230ca924866d43add6a484cbacbf816c20","tid":2058151,"uid":205733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T02:52:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: blue;\"><ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">中共如意算盤：借經濟低迷用低價收購港企，藉此完全控制香港各行各業，政治審查所有人</span></strong></ins></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">但中共最錯既，就係大撒幣式收購企業<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢選擇收購/泵水既企業，究竟係經濟周期/社會運動 以致虧損<br />\n定係本身 business model 出現問題以致虧損？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>- 若果係